________________________________________
8 Group Policy Object (GPO) Configuration
________________________________________

🏛️ Create and Link a GPO
New-GPO -Name "SecurityBaseline" -Comment "Hardening settings for all domain users"
New-GPLink -Name "SecurityBaseline" -Target "OU=IT,DC=vlab,DC=local"

🔐 Common Settings
•	Enforce password complexity and length:
o	Computer Configuration > Policies > Windows Settings > Security Settings > Account Policies > Password Policy
•	Disable local admin access:
o	Computer Configuration > Preferences > Control Panel Settings > Local Users and Groups

🧹 Deploy Logon Banner
User Configuration > Policies > Admin Templates > System > Logon > Display user message
________________________________________
9️⃣ Delegation of Control
________________________________________
🔧 Delegate OU Permissions

1.	In Active Directory Users and Computers, right-click the OU (e.g., IT).
2.	Select Delegate Control.
3.	Choose the user/group to delegate.
4.	Choose common tasks or custom task → allow permissions like:
o	Reset user passwords
o	Create/delete user accounts

🛑 View Delegation
Get-Acl "AD:\OU=IT,DC=vlab,DC=local" | Format-List
________________________________________
🔗 10️⃣ Domain & Forest Trusts
________________________________________
📍 Create Trusts

Trusts require at least 2 domains/forests. Example: vlab.local & corp.local
1.	Open Active Directory Domains and Trusts.
2.	Right-click your domain → Properties → Trusts → New Trust.
3.	Enter the name of the other domain.
4.	Choose trust type:
o	External Trust
o	Forest Trust
o	Shortcut Trust
5.	Choose direction:
o	One-way: Incoming or Outgoing
o	Two-way

🔄 Verify Trusts
nltest /domain_trusts
________________________________________
⚙️ 11️⃣ Advanced Configurations
________________________________________

🧩 Fine-Grained Password Policies (FGPP)
New-ADFineGrainedPasswordPolicy -Name "AdminsPolicy" \
 -Precedence 1 -MinPasswordLength 12 -PasswordComplexityEnabled $true \
 -LockoutThreshold 5 -LockoutDuration "00:30:00" \
 -LockoutObservationWindow "00:30:00" -ReversibleEncryptionEnabled $false

Add-ADFineGrainedPasswordPolicySubject -Identity "AdminsPolicy" -Subjects "CN=Domain Admins,CN=Users,DC=vlab,DC=local"
🔄 Replication Schedule
Set-ADReplicationSiteLink -Identity "DEFAULTIPSITELINK" -ReplicationFrequencyInMinutes 15
💬 Add Company Info Banner (Legal Notice)
Computer Configuration > Policies > Windows Settings > Security Settings > Local Policies > Security Options
- Interactive logon: Message title
- Interactive logon: Message text
